accessibility.text: Dan is a Software Architect for a major financial institute and has an extensive technical background working with companies such as Google, IBM, Microsoft, Samsung, & FaceBook.

He holds degrees and certifications from Stanford in Computer Science, Artificial Intelligence, Machine Learning, and Computational Linguistics. He also has degrees International Business and Marketing from AIU.
Creatively speaking, Dan has produced shows for NYFW - creating imaginative and immersive experiences including the first VR Fashion Show with Samsung.
Dan is super excited because this project will allow him to provide technical and creative expertise, resources, and support across all aspects of the hub.
